OL,2,MA practical guide to internet
OL,4,Mdefamation (or: what not to do after
OL,6,Myou've defamed someone)
OL,8,CMatthew Garrett
OL,9,CSun 18:00-18:30
OL,10,CStage B
OL,12,GIt turns out that you can't just say
OL,13,Ganything on the internet. Things that
OL,14,Gwould be illegal to put in print are
OL,15,Galso illegal to publish online. We'll
OL,16,Gbe going on a short journey through a
OL,17,Greal world case of this, from the
OL,18,Gprocess of starting a claim to turning
OL,19,Gup in the high court and what happens
OL,20,Gnext. It'll be a cautionary story
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
